he API but backed by optional `io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2`; testing it without adding that dependency may fail.\",\n    \"POJO JSON mapping via `sendJson(Object)` may require optional Jackson databind behavior; `sendJsonObject` avoids that setup while still covering normal JSON request usage.\",\n    \"Local Gradle/native-image verification remains authoritative for whether the Netty runtime properties are sufficient.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0dfa6b2adfbe6ba9016a401af953e48190b153e325847dd6ff\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1159, "output": 1384, "cacheRead": 35840, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 38383, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782586086137, "responseId": "resp_0dfa6b2adfbe6ba9016a401ae6dd708190b01c276f22cfdf45"}, "toolResults": []}
